<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Welcome to Baytul Mutun!</h2>
    
    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for registering with Baytul Mutun. To complete your registration and verify your email address, please click the button below:</p>
    
    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
    
    <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p>{{verificationUrl}}</p>
    
    <p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    
    <p>If you did not create an account with Baytul Mutun, please ignore this email.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Baytul Mutun Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
